        "**Multiply by 10 (one digit of repeat).** $10x = 6.6666\\ldots$.",
        "**Subtract to CANCEL the repeating tail.** $10x - x = 6.6666\\ldots - 0.6666\\ldots = 6$ (the tails are identical and cancel).",
